      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 36 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>明夷，利艱貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Ming Yi indicates that (in the circumstances which it denotes) it will be advantageous to realise the difficulty (of the position), and maintain firm correctness.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
