      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 36 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：明夷于南狩，得其大首，不可疾貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows its subject, (in the condition indicated by) Ming Yi, hunting in the south, and taking the great chief (of the darkness). He should not be eager to make (all) correct (at once).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
