      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四：入于左腹，獲明夷之心，出于門庭。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth six, divided, shows its subject (just) entered into the left side of the belly (of the dark land). (But) he is able to carry out the mind appropriate (in the condition indicated by) Ming Yi, quitting the gate and courtyard (of the lord of darkness).</seg>
      </tuv>
