        <seg>六五：箕子之明夷，利貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth six, divided, shows how the count of K? fulfilled the condition indicated by Ming Yi. It will be advantageous to be firm and correct.</seg>
