      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六：不明晦，初登于天，后入于地。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The sixth six, divided, shows the case where there is no light, but (only) obscurity. (Its subject) had at first ascended to (the top of) the sky; his future shall be to go into the earth.</seg>
